items.headline: Welcome to the Electric Company Wiki
items.desc:
Welcome to the main page of The Electric Company Wikia! We have over 290 pages of everything about the Electric Company.

The Electric Company is a children's educational program on PBS Kids GO!, derived from the classic 1971 series. The series premiered as a four episode mini-marathon on PBS on January 19, 2009, then became a weekly series with an episode shown each Friday. Like the original, this version is produced by Sesame Workshop.

We're always looking for new help on making this wiki as great and truthful as ever. Please sign up and share what you know about the Electric Company this wiki!
